data.description: Hunting for a super cute Cape Cod in West Akron? We've got one that you're going to want to check out! This 3-bedroom property is currently a rental property but serves you with plenty of options to continue renting or to make it a home of your own. Great curb appeal, two-car attached garage and we love an enclosed front porch. Inside you'll love the easy layout, spacious primary bedroom, hardwood floors, and the finished attic. Located just around the corner from W Market Street and all that West Akron has to offer, great homes like this don't stay on the market long, so act fast and schedule your showing today!
